{"tid":1898232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［警世］開心完了未？對家做緊野！！！","createTime":"2020-02-26T04:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T09:09:12.000Z","uid":247494,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0ddbed189062f2a27d40342c5e2c3267d21f838a","tid":1898232,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"劏房波咁撚孤寒都肯全民派一萬，對家即刻衝出認，你地係度做？<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地係度打飛機！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n之後的施政報告，一定有好多益廢老、藍營的措施，目的係咩？對家明顯係9月立會造勢，先有咁既部署，仲要係咁出招！你班連登仔仲係度嘈緊體制內/外的抗爭！對家雖人數少，但係團結過你地，你地知唔知醜！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地之前派口罩咁又點？對家個個派一萬，港豬即刻連你地做咩都唔記得！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點拆招？我地梗係照攞一萬，仲要係快！我地要開動文宣，審視過去廿幾年，少數派做過幾多次派錢野，同埋叫身邊廢老唔好投佢地：原來咁架，佢地今次選唔到，再下屆咪爭取全民2萬？<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64498233cb4bf159d88326da8f1ea8513c0bb78","tid":1898232,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:24:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41455e93e8ee3acc4035278b73978c8ac53694b4","tid":1898232,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:25:08.000Z","msg":"推啊推啊"},{"pid":"7867fea44bc355439a3b2add8940a22e4b5ce5d8","tid":1898232,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:26:17.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"56648940faad44e6cabfeb75f52a127d7785a568","tid":1898232,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:26:50.000Z","msg":"係咪忘記晒所有手足的犧牲"},{"pid":"64b05df226578c0978bf1dbcc29c7c578d4cc322","tid":1898232,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:27:05.000Z","msg":"忘記晒我就日日提"},{"pid":"a5005f347b27ca8b7fd6a8b3a06f29fab942fc02","tid":1898232,"uid":101906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:27:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a335db1a51233076090004280387ae6cd2